# The vendor-distributed P4Python zip (re-downloadable from Perforce)
**/p4python-*-x64-whl.zip

# Python bytecode
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]

# C++ build artifacts (accel/ samples compile here)
**/_build/
*.obj
*.exe
*.pdb
*.ilk

# FASTBuild: vendor binaries (re-download via accel/tools/fastbuild/README.md)
# + machine-specific generated config + dependency DB
accel/tools/fastbuild/FBuild*.exe
accel/tools/fastbuild/LICENSE.TXT
**/_generated.bff
*.fdb

# Vendored bgfx/bx/bimg source trees (Track 3 workload tier).
